Package: synthesizer
Type: Package
Title: Synthesize sounds, melodies, chords, and stochastic compositions
Version: 0.1.0
Author: S. Hill
Maintainer: S. Hill <52792611+shill1729@users.noreply.github.com>
Description: Synthesize soundwaves and stochastic compositions using R functions.
    Features include producing stochastic fugues, counterpoint, minimalist compositions and random harmonics, rhythms and pitches
    according to Markov chains or other stochastic processes like random walks and Brownian motions.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports: stats, markovChains, seewave, tuneR
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
